<font face=Arial size=-1 color=black><div class=titlebar>Vulnerability Loop</div>

<div class=itemtext>This is one of 4 original-series games that has a non-loop pattern.  It actually has 2 loops, one of 3 robots and one of 5.  Also, Magnet Man has 2 vulnerabilities.  It should also be mentioned that all of the MM3 Robo Masters are vulnerable to their own weapon.
<p>Spark -> Magnet -> Hard -> Top -> Spark -> Shadow -> Magnet
<br>Snake -> Gemini -> Needle -> Snake<br><br></div><div class=titlebar>Beginner's Level Orders</div>

<div class=itemtext>You'll need to fight just 2 Robot Masters with the plasma cannon with this level order.  Magnet Man is fairly easy, and has the best weapon in the game, and Snake Man's weapon is great in Top Man's stage.
<p>Magnet -> Hard -> Snake -> Top -> Spark -> Shadow -> Gemini -> Needle<br><br></div><div class=titlebar>Advanced Level Order</div>

<div class=itemtext>If you're planning to use the plasma cannon against most or all of the bosses, this level order will keep you equipped with the best weapons possible for each level.
<p>Magnet -> Snake -> Shadow -> Top -> Hard -> Gemini -> Needle -> Spark<br><br></div></font></td></tr></table>

